{"tid":1845804,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【行動】立即connect怕死藍絲發起400萬倒林鄭爭普選遊行","createTime":"2020-01-27T10:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T11:20:54.000Z","uid":312125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb938fe0450f227533e8553c91f9cfc0202d81ba","tid":1845804,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次特區政府完全唔理藍絲民意，放強國人落香港醫病，<br />\n身邊藍絲大為憤概，今次正係connect藍絲嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議以新團體名義，例如關注武漢肺炎爭普選大聯盟，申請兩路大遊行，港島路線為禮賓府及中聯辦，九龍路線為西九龍高鐵站，發起四百萬黃藍團結大遊行。<br />\n當香港黃藍團結之後，共產黨一定會非常懼怕，會採取更強烈行動，多做多錯，最後盡失民心，而香港最終會得到真普選甚至獨立。<br />\n<br />\n呢段時間請文宣加強造勢，團結怕死及有樓有舖嘅非地下黨核心嘅藍絲<br />\n請幫忙推post置頂🔝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248cb4b26d4a19d1260c3a29347f4543249c8392","tid":1845804,"uid":75870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"怕死藍絲點會同你出黎行<br />\n<br />\n發起全民罷工就差唔多 大把人初5開工 邊個敢啊"},{"pid":"f1237e87f68c5643dae3047f76fe9e6e0ffd6f16","tid":1845804,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"要求搞返個撐武漢集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec03aa88ede7735af188bd6771e417dba938b03","tid":1845804,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"248cb4b26d4a19d1260c3a29347f4543249c8392","tid":1845804,"uid":75870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"怕死藍絲點會同你出黎行<br />\n<br />\n發起全民罷工就差唔多 大把人初5開工 邊個敢啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"罷工保平安"},{"pid":"b831941cae661015288bda9955c69503119cd153","tid":1845804,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"